OL,3,CChampion horse trainer jailed for
OL,4,Cthree years for assaulting dog walker
OL,6,FA champion horse trainer has been
OL,7,Fjailed for three years for attacking a
OL,8,F72-year old dog walker who was on his
OL,9,Fland.
OL,11,FRichard Evan Rhys Williams, known as
OL,12,FEvan Williams, 55, repeatedly struck
OL,13,FMartin Dandridge, with a hockey stick
OL,14,Fduring the assault.
OL,16,FThe incident occurred on the evening
OL,17,Fof December 4th 2024 when Mr Dandridge
OL,18,Fwas mistaken for a poacher.
