OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1776345056
OL,3,CChampion horse trainer jailed for
OL,4,Cthree years for assaulting dog walker
OL,6,FDog walker, Mr Dandridge, from
OL,7,FSwindon, Wiltshire, suffered injuries
OL,8,Fincluding a fractured arm on Williams'
OL,9,Fland at Llancarfan, Vale of Glamorgan,
OL,10,FSouth Wales.
OL,12,FThe defendant denied a charge of
OL,13,Fcausing grievous bodily harm with
OL,14,Fintent, but was convicted by a
OL,15,Funanimous jury following a trial at
OL,16,FCardiff Crown Court in March.
OL,18,FOn Tuesday, Recorder Angharad Price
OL,19,Fsentenced Williams to three years in
OL,20,Fprison.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
