PN,46803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1776345056
OL,3,CChampion horse trainer jailed for
OL,4,Cthree years for assaulting dog walker
OL,6,FShe told Williams: "This is an
OL,7,Fappalling offence where you attacked
OL,8,FMr Dandridge causing him serious
OL,9,Finjuries.
OL,11,F"I know that you fully understand that
OL,12,Fhe is still living with the impact of
OL,13,Fyour actions on that day 16 months
OL,14,Fago."
OL,16,FThe judge highlighted that Williams
OL,17,Fhad a "choice" that day, either to
OL,18,Fconfront Mr Dandridge himself or wait
OL,19,Ffor nearby police to attend.
OL,26,@nD@TOUsD@AOUvD@EO]yD@GOUyD@NO]
