PN,46804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1776345056
OL,3,CChampion horse trainer jailed for
OL,4,Cthree years for assaulting dog walker
OL,6,FShe said, "When you gave evidence at
OL,7,Ftrial, you talked very passionately of
OL,8,Fyour champion racehorses and their
OL,9,Fsecurity, you talked of protecting
OL,10,Fthem from harm".
OL,12,F"You also talked about protecting your
OL,13,Ffamily from harm. However, that
OL,14,Fprotection should not have came at Mr
OL,15,FDandridge's cost."
OL,17,FThe judge also described an incident
OL,18,Fthat took place six weeks before the
OL,19,Fassault, where Williams disturbed
OL,20,Fpoachers on his land and threatened
OL,21,Fthem with a shotgun.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@OO]tD@AOUwD@RO]
