PN,46805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1776345056
OL,3,CChampion horse trainer jailed for
OL,4,Cthree years for assaulting dog walker
OL,6,FShe stated, "The earlier incident you
OL,7,Fexperienced with threats of violence
OL,8,Fto you and your home must have been
OL,9,Fvery frightening."
OL,11,F"It is never acceptable to take the
OL,12,Flaw into your own hands. This sentence
OL,13,Fwill be a lesson to you that it is
OL,14,Falways better to call the police if
OL,15,Fyou think a crime is being committed."
OL,26,@nD@MOUqD@RO]sD@AOUwD@fO]
